public:
    int flipLights(int n, int presses) {
        if (presses == 0) return 1;
        if (n == 1) return 2;
        if (n == 2) return presses == 1 ? 3 : 4;
        if (presses == 1) return 4;
        if (presses == 2) return 7;
        return 8;
    }
};```
efficiency: HIGH
time complexity: O(1)
space complexity: O(1)
energy implications: LOW
explanation: After 3 presses the state space saturates at 8 distinct patterns regardless of n≥3; earlier cases are handled by direct enumeration.

